name: Boys Sky Blue Martian Bodysuit
description:
Sky blue "Mummy's little martian" applique bodysuits are cut from 100% cotton fabric and fused to the bodysuit. They have been straight stitched around the edges to minimise fraying.

Bodysuits are 100% cotton and have an envelope neck.  They have press stud fastening at the bottom.

All items come gift wrapped.  Machine wash in a 40 degree cycle inside out. Do not tumble dry. Minimal fraying will occur, but this adds to its character.
